args: Agreed! Now we rush them down!
Obviously! I'll take point.\nMake sure you keep up!
Ugh, that STILL wasn't enough?\nLearn to take a hint and just DIE already!
Our blows are definitely landing, but this\nspecimen seems far sturdier than the one\nI faced—and I have a hunch as to why.
Yes. It's thanks to the little lady's blood it\nabsorbed. I have to admit I'm impressed\nat just how potent a trueblood's essence is.
Stop praising the thing and help me think\nof a plan. There must be a way out of this!
We need to exhaust its energy or destroy\nthe core in one go, and we're not equipped\nto do either.
Even if the prince shapeshifts, we\nstill lack for a decisive final blow.
Then stand back and let me do it.
Just ask my bloodkin how awesome I am\nwhen I go all out. He's seen it firsthand.
I have, but... I thought that power was lost\nto you.
Maybe so, but I've still got the next\nbest thing. I'm a vampire, after all!
Just what are you planning to do?
I'm gonna need a little blood, buster. With\na sip of your life juice, I'll be unstoppable!
What?! You can't be serious. My blood is—
Too strong for me? Basically poison? Duh.\nSo I'll writhe in pain a little. Big whoop.
I just need to grit my teeth and bear it, and\nI'll have all the power I could ever need!\nI'm ready for you.
Don't worry. You know I've grown.\nWE'VE grown. I won't let myself be\ndomineered by a little blood this time!
Doesn't look like it's going to wait patiently\nwhile we discuss the matter, Prince.
He's right. This stalemate won't last long.\nWhat's your call, {player_name}?
Do you still not trust me?
I can handle it. I'm ready for this.\nPlease, just believe in me.
...It's true. You ARE stronger than I think.\nAll right. If you say you're ready, I'll take\nyou at your word.
Here—take the blood from this wound.
Vania! Are you all right?!\nWas the blood still too much?!
Just...took me by surprise a bit. But I'm all\nright now. I can feel the power surging!
Okay, abyss seed! Time for a taste of what\nI can REALLY do!
The seed's broken apart—it's detaching\nfrom its host! You've actually done it...\nRemarkable. It's finished, then.
All the mana is converging on one point...\nThis is bad! The seed is using the last of\nits power to attack the little lady!
What?! Rrgh, we can't reach her in time!\nRun, Vania!
...The seed's gone silent.\nAll that's left is a husk.
*cough* *pant* Good. We managed\nto stop it. Are you all right, Vania?
I'm great. You gave me your blood,\nAND you shielded me.
...Heh heh. I never doubted you would.\nI guess our bond won out in the end.
Without a doubt. This victory was won\nthrough our teamwork. We can finally\nbreathe easy.
The Halidom, a few days after the seed's\ndestruction...
Blooodkiiin, I've got nothing to do today.\nEntertain me!
Very well. Shall we read a picture book?\nOr perhaps you fancy another go at chess?
Hmmm, those both sound fun,\nbut what I'd REALLY like to do is...
Hello to the Halidom's newest BFFs.
Uncle Sparky! You said you were off to\ninvestigate the incident. Did you finish?
We got about as far as we're able for now.\nAnd along the way, we came across a key\npiece of information... Yurius?
I'll get right to the point. A portion of the\nseed's husk was taken from the scene. We\ndon't know by whom, or where they went.
Seriously?! We went to all that trouble to\ndestroy the thing, and someone swiped it?
We were distracted by our injuries at the\ntime, but still... Escaping with the seed\namid that chaos? It must've been planned.

If that's the case, though, why were
they so sloppy in their execution?
Did my brother know all along the
seed would be destroyed?

Most likely. However it ended, it was a
useful experiment for him. After all,
simply possessing the seeds poses
an undeniable danger to the holder.
If he proved able to control them, he wins;\nif the seed was destroyed, it still has its\nuses. I expect he calculated as much.
I see. Then my brother still has some sort\nof scheme up his considerable sleeves.
Meaning that we can't sit idly by. Yurius\nand I will continue to pursue the matter.
Huh. Sounds like you guys have your plates\nfull, then.
Very. Things worked out this time around\nthanks to your help, but there's no telling\nwhat will happen next time.
Well... If something does come up,\nmy bloodkin and I will make a special\nexception and lend you a hand.
Sure. You gave me some pretty solid\nadvice about strengthening our bond.
Which is SUPER strong now, by the way.\nSo yeah... Thanks. I owe you a little favor\nor two for that!
I don't recall giving you any advice.\nDid HE say something to you?\n...Yurius, playing relationship counselor?
No comment, Captain. Now, little lady,\nI bid you be well. I look forward to another\ndisplay of the future queen's power.
It's a date! My bloodkin and I are gonna be\npractically attached at the hip by then, so\nget ready for a REAL show.
Invest in some garters now, because it's\ngonna blow your socks clean off. Right,\nbloodkin? Tell the man!
Vania speaks true. Our bond IS stronger\nthan ever before, after all.
Yeah! So whatever comes our way, the two\nof us are gonna be juuust fine. Count on it!
